        "subject": "DDN-99 llite: accept user set dir stripe with known value",
        "message": "DDN-99 llite: accept user set dir stripe with known value\n\nUser can set dir xattr with known pattern value, such as rsync with\n-X option.\n\nMake lod_verify_striping() accept lov stripe from user and its\npattern is LOV_PATTERN_RAID0.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I00d552d48fa4235cdbf45afb8b303272fa5d01e0\n"
